The LORD is my shepherd
I have all that I need
Lets me rest in green meadows
he leads me beside peaceful streams
He renews my strength
guides me along
The right paths
bring honor to
his name
Even when I walk
through dark valleys
I won’t be afraid
you’re close beside me

Your rod and your staff
protect and comfort me
You prepare a feast for me
in the presence of my enemies
You honor me
Anointing
my head with oil
My cup overflows
with blessings
Even when I walk
through darkest valleys
I won’t be afraid
you’re close beside me

The LORD is my shepherd. I have all I need  - Psalm 23
